{"tid":2512650,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 14.6 正式版有機會連同 Apple Music Hi-Fi 版推出","createTime":"2021-05-02T02:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T03:06:48.000Z","uid":131807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"98d1abfd19adc733cc92ef2a72f54efd512fb095","tid":2512650,"uid":131807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"網站 Hits Double Daily 昨日引述音樂業界人士指，Apple Music 將會在未來數星期推出 Hi-Fi 版，顧名思義 Hi-Fi 版將會主打超高音質，目標用戶是對音質有高要求的音樂發燒友。消息指 Apple Music Hi-Fi 版本的收費將會與普通版相同，美國市場依然是 9.99 美元（香港的月費則為 HK$58）。<br />\n <br />\n收費維持不變   Apple Music Hi-Fi 版短期內推出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國網站 9to5mac 在 iOS 14.6 Beta 的 Music 程式發現，程式碼出現 Dolby Audio、Dolby Atmos 和 Loseless，相信是 Apple Music 準備提供無損音樂和支援兩種 Dolby 音效，9to5mac 估計 Apple Music Hi-Fi 版會連同 iOS 14.6 在本月內提供。<br />\n <br />\n不過 Hits Double Daily 則有另一想法，他們相信 Apple Music Hi-Fi 版很大機會在 6 月 7 日揭幕的 WWDC 公佈，Apple 還有望同場發表 AirPods 3 無線耳機。"},{"pid":"9b0969e1504179abe394ce46a66a9b1b6b4cc806","tid":2512650,"uid":137393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:29:41.000Z","msg":"正 WWDC會唔會支持AAC以上CODEC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a385efd0f33826ac61f2ee1afd1a7848b83cc5","tid":2512650,"uid":240333,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"用YouTube music都好過垃圾Apple music<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbf99c1c3164f26c136fdfb15a1817af82c6b70","tid":2512650,"uid":48330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93a385efd0f33826ac61f2ee1afd1a7848b83cc5","tid":2512650,"uid":240333,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"用YouTube music都好過垃圾Apple music<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=